V0503_01_00_00_0.text: Gong is gonna use his Heavystrong Style to win this Duel!

V0503_01_00_01_0.text: Every Duel is a chance to hone Gong's Heavystrong Style!

V0503_01_00_02_0.text:
Gong won't go easy on ya!
That's how Gong shows respect!

V0503_01_00_03_0.text: Gong's got too much pride to lose this Duel!

V0503_01_00_04_0.text: Gong's gotta try new things if Gong wants to defeat you!

V0503_01_00_05_0.text:
Bring it on!
Gong isn't hard to find!

V0503_01_00_05_1.text: Gong'll be standing right here to face you head on!

V0503_03_00_00_0.text:
Gong isn't about mercy!
Get ready!

V0503_03_00_01_0.text: Gong is just getting warmed up!

V0503_03_00_02_0.text:
You're pretty tough!
That makes you a good opponent!

V0503_03_00_04_0.text: Things look tough, but Gong's been in worse!

V0503_03_00_05_0.text: Gong's never gonna abandon his Heavystrong Style!

V0503_05_00_00_0.text:
Duels aren't about luck!
They're about believing in your cards!

V0503_06_01_00_0.text: Gong's been waiting for you to do that!

V0503_07_09_00_0.text: Gong flips over a Set card!

V0503_11_01_00_0.text: Gong summons a monster in Defense Position!

V0503_11_08_01_0.text:
Gong builds the Overlay Network!
Xyz Summon!

V0503_16_00_01_0.text: Gong says this Duel is over, friendo!

V0503_20_01_01_0.text: Gong is gonna Set this card!

V0503_21_00_00_0.text: Gong's strategy is now in motion!

V0503_21_00_01_0.text: Gong will stop your attack with his Heavystrong Style!

V0503_21_00_03_0.text: You should quit making moves and sit on your strategy!

V0503_21_00_04_0.text: Panicking is only gonna make things worse!

V0503_21_00_05_0.text: Gong has much more to give!

V0503_28_00_00_0.text: Stand strong to win - that's the Heavystrong Style's motto!!

V0503_28_00_01_0.text: Gong believes in his cards, so Gong's cards believe in him!

V0503_28_00_02_0.text: In a Duel, you're battling against your deepest fears!

V0503_28_00_02_1.text: So you can't win if you don't believe in yourself!

V0503_28_00_03_0.text: Gong is strong like oak - and flexible like oak!

V0503_28_00_04_0.text: Even the Heavystrong Style has to evolve with the times!

V0503_29_00_00_0.text: Gong needs to get back to training to avoid losing again!

V0503_29_00_01_0.text: What does Gong have to do to improve his game?

V0503_29_00_02_0.text:
Gong lost focus near the end.
Gong can't have that!

V0503_29_00_03_0.text:
You brought the best out of Gong.
Thanks, friendo.

V0503_29_00_04_0.text: Gong isn't ashamed to lose to a great Duelist like you!

V0503_29_00_05_0.text:
You actually made Gong take a step back!
Well done!

V0503_33_00_00_0.text: The Heavystrong Style lets Gong execute this strategy!

V0503_33_00_01_0.text: The heart and soul of the Heavystrong Style!

V0503_33_00_02_0.text: Gong is evolving the Heavystrong Style!

V0503_34_00_00_0.text: Gong don't steal techniques! Gong learns 'em!

V0503_34_00_03_0.text: Hey, pay attention! You're in the middle of a Duel!

V0503_34_00_04_0.text: Giving your best is the least you can do!

V0503_34_00_06_0.text: You're a worthy foe - you don't make any pointless moves.

V0503_34_00_07_0.text: Action Cards are too random to rely on!

V0503_34_00_08_0.text: The strong don't need to be flexible!

V0503_34_00_09_0.text: You can't win running around like a crazy chicken!

V0503_36_00_04_0.text: Gong passes the baton to you, Zuzu!
